{"tid":1809244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警差啲又砌生豬肉成功 64歲被告仍判感化15個月","createTime":"2020-01-03T02:59:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T03:08:17.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e85400db50d5f5b9c1fb048182eaa61d5fefc078","tid":1809244,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T02:59:58.000Z","msg":"去年10月14日中環遮打花園集會之後，一名六旬男子被指用手推車撞凹警車，被控刑事毀壞罪。  <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">辯方日前找到事發時片段，證明被告並非撞凹警車之黑衣人</span></span></strong>，當時片段只拍到被告曾以手推車推向警車方向，但該位置並無損毀。  控方之後改控「企圖刑毀」罪，64歲被告認罪，今早（1月3日）在東區裁判法院被判感化15個月。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-03-2020/58783\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F01-03-2020%2F58783&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7C9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=038731be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-03-2020/58783</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2019"},{"pid":"3fad3491a7fc34bc25185c4c85499b54cec0284f","tid":1809244,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T03:00:52.000Z","msg":"認罪做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇損壞都認"},{"pid":"ff16fd6ecd3c18e899f2ff6782e582a53f28cbf0","tid":1809244,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T03:08:17.000Z","msg":"企圖刑毀 又係啲咩垃圾罪黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}